  "title": "feat(insights): option to disable automatic insights middleware",
  "body": "instead of passing your own middleware, where timing could be tricky, to disable the internal middleware you pass `insights: false` to InstantSearch. Note that the internal middleware will still be removed when a different middleware is passed to allow easy customisation\r\n\r\nFX-2250",
